OL,3,CMan dies following road crash in north
OL,4,CBelfast
OL,6,FA man has died following a road crash
OL,7,Fin north Belfast in March.
OL,9,FPolice said the death follows a
OL,10,Fcollision involving a car and a
OL,11,Fpedestrian in the Shankill Road area
OL,12,Fon Saturday March 28.
OL,14,FA police spokesperson issued a public
OL,15,Fappeal for information.
OL,17,F"At approximately 9.45am, police
OL,18,Freceived a report of a collision
OL,19,Finvolving a car and a pedestrian in
OL,20,Fthe Shankill Road area," they said.
