OL,3,CMan dies following road crash in north
OL,4,CBelfast
OL,6,F"Officers attended, together with
OL,7,Fcolleagues from other emergency
OL,8,Fservices, but sadly the man has since
OL,9,Fdied in hospital from his injuries.
OL,11,F"Our enquiries are continuing, and we
OL,12,Fwould appeal to anyone who witnessed
OL,13,Fthe collision, or who may have digital
OL,14,Ffootage which could assist with our
OL,15,Finvestigation, to contact the
OL,16,FCollision Investigation Unit on 101,
OL,17,Fquoting reference number 344 28/03/26."
